Title: Nature Persists
Description:
Admittedly, I do not know what to do next.

If he is to rest here... flowers would be lovely.

The podlings in this area have been hiding among the flowers. Retrieve seeds from them, Champion, and I will make them bloom.

I think Gracus will like the flowers.
ObjectivesText: Collect 6 Sprouted Seedlings from Sneaky Podlings.
